      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:04:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者正在寻求股票回购以维持美国股市的运转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/investors-are-looking-to-share-buybacks-to-keep-us-stock-market-afloat-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年伊始，股市表现疲软。但随着财报季的开始以及公司开始宣布股票回购计划，这种情况可能会在本周发生变化，投资者希望这将有助于市场保持去年的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/investors-are-looking-to-share-buybacks-to-keep-us-stock-market-afloat-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国各地数百架航班因暴风雨而取消</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/hundreds-of-flights-canceled-over-a-pair-of-storms-across-the-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两场冬季风暴导致纽约哈德逊河谷积雪超过一英尺，并引发了大平原地区的暴风雪警告，导致美国各地数百架航班停飞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/hundreds-of-flights-canceled-over-a-pair-of-storms-across-the-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 14:35:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
